      ("17 compile-broken files") + Wave 1 outcome (compile already clean) means 011 is
      compile-only; the RUNTIME failures (the 53) are this task's responsibility per design §7.
      Sibling-coordination caveat (per design §2.3 + NFR-04): Communications has HIGHEST
      sibling-project risk (x-email-communication-solution-r2). The Phase 0 task 005
      priority-order sign-off must explicitly cover the increased Communications scope BEFORE
      this task dispatches. See `notes/handoffs/phase23-scope-delta-2026-05-31.md`.

      Effort impact: ~3-5h additional vs. original 2-3h estimate. If overflow expected, owner
      may split into batch 1a (AssociationMapping 29) + batch 1b (DataverseRecord 23) + retain
      batch 2 (056) for remaining + ArchivalFlow (1).
    </scope-extension>
